About
=====

  The qt-gui directory contains the primesieve GUI application
  developed with the Qt framework (http://qt.nokia.com/products/).

Qt project file (MSVC, GCC, Intel ICC)
======================================

  * primesieve.pro
    primesieve project file to be used with the Qt-Creator IDE (e.g.
    to edit the source code or build a primesieve executable).

Source files
============

  * src/PrimeSieveGUI.cpp & .h
    Contains the graphical user interface code.
  * src/PrimeSieveGUI_menu.cpp
    Contains code related to the menu bar of the GUI.
  * src/PrimeSieveProcess.cpp & .h
    Class that is used for prime sieving. PrimeSieveProcess launches
    a ParallelPrimeSieve instance in a separate process, this approach
    allows to easily cancel the sieving process.
    The communication between the GUI process (PrimeSieveGUI) and
    PrimeSieveProcess is realised via shared memory.
  * src/main.cpp
    Contains the ParallelPrimeSieve code launched by a
    PrimeSieveProcess object.
